                    "The worthiest form of worship is the most hidden one. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "The worth of a Muslims properties is as much as his bloods. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "The worst places to sit in are roads and bazaars markets. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
