                    "The reward of the one who donates something in affluence does not exceed that of the needy receiver. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "The refractoriness of a child in childhood will result in the development of his intellect in adulthood. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "The reduction in your servants tasks will be a reward added to your book of deeds in the Day of Doom. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
