                    "The Quran is healer of mans spiritual maladies. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "The Quran is like unto a tied camel whose owner may keep it intact by holding it as it is, or let it go away by releasing its rope Muhamad ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
