                    "Give alms, for it surely releases you from the Fire. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "Gifts impair ears, eyes and hearts. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "Gifts blind men of wisdom. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "Gifts are sustenance from God and so, whoever is offered a gift should accept it. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
