                    "Flattery is not an attribute of a true believer. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "Fire Hell will be the abode of a person whose tongue frightens people. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "Find pretext to pardon the faults of the fair, generous people. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
                    "Fever makes ones sin fall just as trees let their leaves fall. ~ Prophet Mohammad (s.a.w)",
