                    "Just as knowledge guides a person and saves him, similarly, ignorance misguides him and destroys him ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "One who gains knowledge (or acts [upon his knowledge]) is rightly guided ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "One who is alone with knowledge does not feel frightened by [his] loneliness ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "One who is alone with knowledge does not feel frightened by [his] loneliness ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "One who acts with knowledge attains his goal and desire from the Hereafter ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Do not make enmity with that which you are ignorant of, for indeed most of knowledge is in that which you don't know ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "There is no guidance for one who has no knowledge ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
