                    "Ask about that which you must know and cannot be excused for being ignorant about ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "The pinnacle of cognizance is fear [of Allah] ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "The end goal of knowledge is tranquillity and forbearance ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Every scholar is fearful [of Allah] ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "When the knowledge of a person increases, his etiquette improves and his awe for his Lord increases ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Knowledge is a refuge ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "The intellect necessitates caution ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Knowledge is a veil [that protects one] from adversities ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Knowledge saves [one] from being entangled in perplexity ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Sharing knowledge [with those who deserve] is the alms-tax of knowledge ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "The fruit of knowledge is worship ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "The fruit of knowledge is acting upon it ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "The wealth of knowledge saves and preserves ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Determination [and resolve] is proportionate to the strength of one's opinion ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
