                    "Vain desire is the enemy of reason ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Vain desire is the bane of the intellects ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Vain desire is the bane of the intellects ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
                    "Vain desire is the partner of blindness ~ Imam Ali (a.s)",
